Package org.midao.jdbc.core.handlers.xml

Interface Summary
XmlHandler Xml handler is responsible for parsing and executing queries from XML files
 

Class Summary
AbstractXmlInputOutputHandler<T> Base implementation of XML input handler
XmlInputOutputHandler<T> Xml Input/Output handler allows executing queries set in XML and loaded into XmlRepositoryFactory.
XmlParameters XML parameters which can be used in XML query
XmlRepositoryFactory XML Repository factory is responsible for reading and caching queries from XML.
